Setup Instructions

1. Go to https://thingspeak.com/ to create Channel and the required details (e.g. field section) in the created Channel

2. Take note of the Channel ID and the Write API Key; you may want to copy and paste these details into the notepad first

3. install the thingspeak library. In terminal, type:

$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get upgrade
$ sudo pip install thingspeak
